Enemies affected by {c_important}{u}Vulnerable{/u}{/c}, Crowd Control, or Shadow Damage over Time are {c_important}Afflicted{/c}, taking {c_number}[SF_7 * 100|x%|]{/c} increased damage from you and your Minions.

Your {c_important}Curse{/c} Skills deal {c_number}{payload:AFFLICTION_PAYLOAD}{/c} Shadow damage when applied to {c_important}Afflicted{/c} enemies. This amount increases by {c_number}[{SF_2}*100|%x|]{/c} of your Damage to Crowd Controlled, {c_important}{u}Vulnerable{/u}{/c} Damage, and Shadow Damage over Time bonuses combined.

Current Damage Bonus: {c_number}[{SF_6}*100|%x|]{/c}
